69713","type":"question","created":1738646291,"answer_count":165,"follower_count":475,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4812,33564,212196],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据财政部网站，2025年2月1日，美国政府宣布以芬太尼等问题为由对所有中国输美商品加征10%关税。美方单边加征关税的做法严重违反世界贸易组织规则，不仅无益于解决自身问题，也对中美正常经贸合作造成破坏。 根据《中华人民共和国关税法》、《中华人民共和国海关法》、《中华人民共和国对外贸易法》等法律法规和国际法基本原则，经国务院批准，自2025年2月10日起，对原产于美国的部分进口商品加征关税。有关事项如下： 一、对煤炭、液化天然气加征15%关税，具体商品范围见附件1。 二、对原油、农业机械、大排量汽车、皮卡加征10%关税，具体商品范围见附件2。 三、对原产于美国的附件所列进口商品，在现行适用关税税率基础上分别加征相应关税，现行保税、减免税政策不变，此次加征的关税不予减免。https://www.mof.gov.cn/zhengwuxinxi/caizhengxinwen/202502/t20250204_3955222.htm"},"attached_info":"CkIIvvDPhaDAh/QnEAMaCTExMzIyNTI4MCCTxoa9BjAAONsDQAJyCzExMjQ2OTY5NzEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"492 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a69f3b01ebff63464a1af1f2eb7b6440_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1738664386.485674","card_id":"Q_436152940","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":436152940,"title":"经常点同一家外卖，商家会知道你是常客吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/436152940","type":"question","created":1608711700,"answer_count":154,"follower_count":383,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6548,11422,15521],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvvDPhaDAh/QnEAMaCDU5MjAxODA5IJT8i/8FMAA4/wJAA3IJNDM2MTUyOTQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"425 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2e471fef034dbeab443